<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <title>Sukuu Activation Email</title>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <style>
    /* styles.css */
    /* Base */
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      min-width: 100%;
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      background-color: #FAFAFA;
      color: #222222;
    }

    a {
      color: #000;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.25;
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    p {
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    table td {
      vertical-align: top;
    }

    /* Layout */
    .email-wrapper {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .email-header {
      background-color: #2f537b;
      color: #FFFFFF;
      padding: 24px;
    }

    .email-body {
      padding: 24px;
      background-color: #FFFFFF;
    }

    .email-footer {
      padding: 24px;
      background-color: #F6F6F6;
    }

    /* Specific Class Styling */
    .sukuu-learning {
      color: #F6F6F6;
    }

    .user-name {
      /* Any specific styling for user's name */
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #0070f3;
      text-transform: capitalize;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .activation-code {
      font-size: 28px;
      color: #0070f3;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }

    /* Buttons */
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #0070f3;
      color: #FFFFFF;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-decoration: none;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="email-wrapper">
    <div class="email-header">
      <h1>Welcome to <span class="sukuu-learning">Sukuu Learning</span></h1>
    </div>
    <div class="email-body">
      <p>Hi <span class="user-name">
          <%= user.name %>,
        </span></p>
      <p>Thanks for signing up for Sukuu Learning! We're excited to have you as an early user.</p>
      <p>Before we get started, we just need to confirm that this is you. Use this activation code:</p>
      <h2 class="activation-code">
        <%= activationCode %>
      </h2>
      <p>Please enter this code on the activation page. The code will expire in 5 minutes.</p>
      <p>If you didn't sign up for Sukuu, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
      <p>Thanks,<br />The Sukuu Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="email-footer">
      <p>You received this email because you signed up for Sukuu. If you didn't sign up, you can safely ignore this
        email.</p>
      <p>Â© 2023 Sukuu, Inc. All rights reserved. Sukuu is a registered trademark of Sukuu, Inc.</p>
      <p>If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact us at <a
          href='mailto:support@sukuu.com'>support@sukuu.com</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>